- Invite your friends to play - agree on time and place together
- Reach all of your disc golf buddies with one message
- Marking scores made as easy and fast as possible
- Can be used online and offline

- Discover nearby disc golf courses where ever you are
- Past games and scores all in one place saved online

Upsi makes it easy to plan to go discing: send a message and agree together on course and time. You don’t have to reach out to each of your disc golf buddies individually. One message to reach them all at once. Never miss a round.

Live games! Get notified whenever a friend is playing. Check the score, current fairway, simple statistics and chat with the group. Cheer them on or comment on the current score. (Sharing images coming later!)

Keep all your past games and scores safe online where they can be found anywhere any time. You can return to the scorecards of your favorite rounds or check out the scores 'from that one time'. When did you last play together and where - easy to find out.

The app is constantly being updated based on the feedback from the users. And it's free to use. Made for disc golfers by disc golfers.

descriptionHtml:
Discover Upsi Disc Golf App!

Unleash the ultimate disc golf experience with the Upsi Disc Golf App! Made for disc golfers by disc golfers, this all-in-one tool offers a seamless blend of convenience, connection, comprehensive features, and now, cutting-edge statistics to elevate your game.

Elevate Your Game with In-Depth Statistics:
- Dynamic Graphs & Insights: Dive into up-to-date statistics and visual graphs to analyze your performance and track improvements.
- Courses & Global Play: Discover which courses and countries you frequent the most and compare with global trends.
- Track Your Commitment: Get insights on how much time you've dedicated to the course, ensuring you're always on top of your game.
- Deep Dive into Gameplay: Review detailed stats on how many games, holes, and throws you've played, both on a yearly and monthly basis.
- Score Mastery: Monitor your overall score and understand your par-relative score development over time to set new personal bests.
- ...And So Much More!: We're always adding new metrics and tools to help you understand your game better.

Why Choose Upsi?
- One-Touch Scoring: Mark your score effortlessly with a single touch. Perfect for on-the-go updates, whether you're teeing off or counting birdies!
- Stay Connected: Plan games, chat in real-time, and share live scores. With Upsi, you can rally your disc golf buddies with just one message, ensuring you never miss out on any action.
- Global Course Directory: Explore over 3,000 disc golf courses worldwide in our course directory! Whether you're looking to tee off at your local course or discover new terrains, our intuitive GPS course directory has you covered. And if you spot an unlisted course, add it in and be a part of our ever-growing community.
- Keep Track: All your games, all your scores - stored securely online. Dive into your game history, revisit those epic moments, and track your progress effortlessly.
- Exclusive Premium Features: With Upsi Black, unlock a treasure trove of features - from private games and specialized game modes like doubles to throw distance measurement and exclusive stats.

Key Features:
- Unified Communication: Send a single message to reach all your disc golf friends and agree on time and course.
- Game Modes Galore: Dive into different game modes like Stroke Play, Match Play, and Skins, available for both individual players and doubles.
- Offline Accessibility: Scorecard works seamlessly both online and offline. Mark scores anytime, anywhere, and sync when you're back online.
- Share Live Games: Keep your friends and fans in the loop with real-time game updates, or choose to keep things private - the choice is yours.
- Always Improving: At Upsi, we value your feedback. Our app is continually evolving to give you the best disc golf experience possible.

Bonus:
- Stay Informed: Receive notifications when a friend hits the course and cheer them on with in-app chat
- Made in Finland: Embrace the finesse of Finnish design, brought to you by passionate disc golf enthusiasts

Dive Deeper into the World of Disc Golf with Upsi:
With its advanced statistics feature, Upsi isn't just an app—it's your personal disc golf coach, analyst, and companion. Whether you're striving to refine your throws or simply enjoy the thrill of frisbee golf, Upsi ensures you have all the tools to make every round count. Download today, and let's chart your path to disc golf mastery! No registration needed to get started.

Proudly keeping score and stats for the disc golf community, one fairway at a time!
